# Frontend (`frontend/`)

Stack: Vue 3 + TypeScript + Vite + Pinia + vue-router + vue-i18n + Tailwind v4. Axios client talks to `/v1`.

| Area | Path |
|------|------|
| Pages | `src/pages/` |
| Layout | `src/layouts/AppLayout.vue` |
| Stores | `src/stores/` — `auth`, `tenant`, `locale` |
| API | `src/services/api.ts`, `src/services/types.ts` |
| i18n | `src/i18n/en/`, `src/i18n/pt-BR/` |
| Composables | `src/composables/` |

## Conventions

- Alias `@/` → `src/`. Build output: `public/build` (`base: '/build/'`); Laravel serves SPA via `resources/views/app.blade.php`.
- Keep `types.ts` aligned with API resources when changing payloads.
- Add user-facing strings to both `en` and `pt-BR` locales.
- Run tooling via containers: `.\scripts\tc.ps1 npm --prefix frontend run test|build` (prefer `--prefix frontend`; root `package.json` is a thin proxy).
- Vitest specs live beside code (`*.spec.ts`). Playwright is a dependency but **not wired** (no e2e config/script yet) — do not assume `tc e2e` works.
